data.description: This charming Cape Cod home has a welcoming floor plan, recently replaced front steps lead you into the living room  which flows through the dining room into the kitchen. There are lovely original hardwood floors throughout most living  space. The kitchen has ample cabinet storage and counter space for those that enjoy cooking, off the kitchen is the  pantry, utility room and half bath. There are also two spacious upstairs bedrooms, with two more downstairs and a shared full bath. The private backyard has a large deck, and patio area perfect for entertaining with some crowd  pleasers, space for outdoor movie night, and raised garden bed. The large detached garage is additional flex space  perfect for office, gym, craft room, workshop or easily converted back into garage. All the big items: water heater,  roof, HVAC, vinyl siding, and windows are newer. Come See Today!
